THE Conference Registration Portal for the NIGERIAN BAR ASSOCIATION's 2015 Annual General Conference (Abuja)

The project uses a MongoDb backend and presumes that the MongoDb driver for Node.js is install globally using `npm
install -g mongodb`

[b]How to Use[/b]

Run `npm install` from the root of the application

Then use `grunt serve` or `node server/app.js` to serve the application